import { useGLTF } from '@react-three/drei'
import { MeshNormalMaterial } from 'three'

export default function Model({ ...props }) {
  const group = useRef()
  const { nodes, materials } = useGLTF('/bike.glb')

    <group ref={group} {...props} dispose={null}>
      <mesh geometry={nodes.Seat.geometry} material={materials.Pedals_Seat} />

      <mesh geometry={nodes.Pedal_Right_Base001.geometry} material={materials.Pedals_Seat} />

      <mesh geometry={nodes.Pedal_Left_Base001.geometry} material={materials.Pedals_Seat} />
      <mesh geometry={nodes.Pedal_Left001.geometry} material={materials.Pedals_Seat} />
      <mesh geometry={nodes.Cranks.geometry} material={materials.Wheel} />
      <mesh geometry={nodes.Cassette.geometry} material={materials.Wheel} />
      <mesh geometry={nodes.Frame.geometry} material={materials.Frame} />
      <mesh geometry={nodes.Wheel_front.geometry} material={materials.Wheel} position={[-0.53, 0.75, 0]} />
      <mesh geometry={nodes.Frame002.geometry} material={materials.Frame} />
      <mesh geometry={nodes.Chain.geometry} material={materials['Chain.001']} position={[0.29, 0.35, -0.05]} scale={[1, 1.03, 1.3]} />
      <meshNormalMaterial attach={"materials"} />
    </group>
  )
}

useGLTF.preload('/bike.glb')
